
<div class="home">
  <div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0), rgba(0,0,0,0)), url('<%= image_path 'banner-bear.jpg' %>')">
    <h1>Your health personalized</h1>
    <h1>to your needs.</h1>
    <div class="content-home">
      <img src="<%= image_path 'arrow-1.png' %>" alt="">
      <div class="buttons">
        <%= link_to "Do the Quiz", categories_path, class: "btn" %>
        <a href="https://www.bol.com/nl/nl/s/?page=1&searchtext=bional&view=tile" class="link-underline">Browse Products</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="disclaimer-banner">Disclaimer** this webpage loads better on your Google Chrome browser.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="marketing-container">
    <div class="marketing-content-container">
      <div class="marketing-title">
        <h2>How it works</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="marketing-images-content">
        <div class="marketing-image-content1">
          <div class="marketing-img marketing-img1">
            <img src="<%= image_path 'girl-melon.jpg' %>" alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="marketing-description">
            <div class="marketing-description-title">
              <h3>Take our quiz</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="marketing-description-body">
              <p>Take our quiz and choose the health categories that you wish to prioritize the most.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="marketing-image-content2">
          <div class="marketing-img marketing-img2">
            <img src="<%= image_path 'avocado2.jpg' %>" alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="marketing-description">
            <div class="marketing-description-title">
              <h3>Tailored results</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="marketing-description-body">
              <p>Based on your results, we create a personalized recommendation of nutrients that you may be lacking in your diet.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="marketing-image-content3">
          <div class="marketing-img marketing-img3">
            <img src="<%= image_path 'girl-oranges.jpg' %>" alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="marketing-description">
            <div class="marketing-description-title">
              <h3>Find the right diet</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="marketing-description-body">
              <p>Receive advice on how to improve your diet, either by adjusting your food choices or by introducing nutrition supplements.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="certifications-container">
    <div class="certifications-images">
      <div class="certification-img">
        <img src="<%= image_path 'organic.png' %>" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="certification-img">
        <img src="<%= image_path 'non-gmo.png' %>" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="certification-img">
        <img src="<%= image_path 'vegan.png' %>" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="certification-img">
        <img src="<%= image_path 'certified.png' %>" alt="">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="background-info-container">
    <div class="background-container1">
      <div class="background-image1">
        <img src="<%= image_path 'flowers.jpg' %>" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="background-content1">
        <div class="background-content-title">
          <h4>A healthier lifestyle.</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="background-content-description">
          <p>At Dr. Bear, we aim to aid individuals in enhancing their health and wellness without requiring a consultation with a dietician. Obtaining all the necessary nutrients for a healthy lifestyle can be challenging.</p>
          <p>By taking our quiz, you can determine the appropriate nutrients to incorporate into your diet, based on your unique health profile. Our objective is to equip you with the knowledge and resources necessary to select a diet that fosters a healthier and more contented life.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="background-content-link" onclick="location.href='<%= about_path %>';">
          <button class="btn btn-ghost">About Us</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="background-info-container2">
    <div class="background-container2">
      <div class="background-image2">
        <img src="<%= image_path 'quiz4.jpg' %>" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="background-content2">
       <div class="background-content-title">
          <h4>Quality Nutrition.</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="background-content-description">
          <p>Although we encourage users to modify their diet, we also provide personalized supplements for those seeking additional support in meeting their nutritional needs. </p>
          <p>We take great care in selecting the finest suppliers for our products. Our rigorous sourcing process ensures that we only work with top-quality suppliers who meet our high standards. Therefore enabling us to maximize both the quality and absorption efficiency of our products, ensuring that our customers receive only the best.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="background-content-link" onclick="location.href='<%= learn_path %>';">
          <button class="btn btn-ghost">Learn More</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="infos">
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-copyright">
        This footer is made with <i class="fas fa-heart"></i> at Le Wagon
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
